Cell["\<\
This problem can be solved by using non-standard Ore algebras which have \
Sin[t] and Cos[t] in the coefficients. The only algorithm that works  \
properly in this setting is Takayama's algorithm. The annihilating ideal has \
to be generated by hand.\
\>", "Text"],

