 RowBox[{"{", 
  RowBox[{"0", ",", 
   FractionBox["1", "2"], ",", "0", ",", 
   RowBox[{"-", 
    FractionBox["5", "2"]}]}], "}"}]], "Output"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
From the fact that the integral is 0 for p=0, we can exclude the first two \
