Cell["\<\
However, if we do not care about the delta part, we find that the principal \
parts agree with the annihilating ideal that is computed for the right-hand \
side:\
\>", "Text"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"pp", "=", 
  RowBox[{"First", "[", 
