Cell["\<\
Since the dimension is 2, theory does not guarantee a telescoping relation. \
However, by inspection we see that the only relation the we have found for \
the summand is already k-free, hence we can do the sum by hand.\
\>", "Text"],

Cell["\<\
A correction term is introduced by the action of S[n] on the summation bound.\
\
\>", "Text"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"corr", "=", 
  RowBox[{"Annihilator", "[", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"Evaluate", "[", 
